  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load knowledge files. Read spec FR-9 + AC-9.</step>
    <step order="2">Read PB-016 reference + current PB-022 stub.</step>
    <step order="3">Author Component Justification block (3-question template).</step>
    <step order="4">Design node graph: Start → LookupUserMembership(sprk_matter) → QueryDataverse (sprk_workassignment WHERE regarding-matter IN membership AND (createdon&gt;=now-24h OR modifiedon&gt;=now-24h)) → CreateNotification.</step>
    <step order="5">Replace stub JSON with full graph. Include Component Justification block.</step>
    <step order="6">Validate via `jps-validate` skill.</step>
    <step order="7">Audit via `jps-playbook-audit` skill.</step>
    <step order="8">Redeploy via `mcp__dataverse__update_record` on PB-022 — set `sprk_configjson`.</step>
    <step order="9">Verify deployment via `mcp__dataverse__read_query`.</step>
    <step order="10">Run `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/`.</step>
    <step order="11">Update `tasks/TASK-INDEX.md`: change task 025 status to ✅.</step>
    <step order="12">Document UAT script + justification in `projects/spaarke-daily-update-service-r4/notes/`.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="mcp-dataverse">update_record — redeploy PB-022; read_query — verify; describe — confirm sprk_workassignment metadata.</tool>
    <tool name="jps-validate">Schema validation</tool>
    <tool name="jps-playbook-audit">Audit against Action catalog</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="code">projects/spaarke-daily-update-service/notes/playbooks/notification-work-assignments.json</output>
    <output type="data">sprk_analysisplaybook PB-022 row sprk_configjson updated</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">notification-work-assignments.json contains functional node graph (no longer stub).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Graph includes LookupUserMembership(sprk_matter) + QueryDataverse (sprk_workassignment) + CreateNotification.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Component Justification block present.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">jps-validate passes.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Deployed PB-022 sprk_configjson matches repo file.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">UAT scenario documented for AC-9.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>Spec FR-9 line 148; AC-9 line 149. Hint: created-or-updated condition (OR createdon, OR modifiedon) covers both new assignments and edits — verify FetchXml supports the OR semantics; if not, document the choice (createdon vs modifiedon) and rationale. Hint: parallel-safe with 022/023/024.</notes>

